id=blockota_twilight
name=Block OTA (twilight CoreELEC dual-boot)
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=partB-installer
description=Disables the Xiaomi OTA updater on every boot so an A/B update cannot overwrite the inactive (CoreELEC) boot/dtbo slot or flip the active slot. Re-applies each boot, so it survives a re-enable; remove the module to restore OTA.
